### Testing Common API
GET http://localhost:5000/auth

### Register Requester
### NOTE: /auth/register now accepts multipart/form-data (for optional profile image upload).
### JSON requests still work (multer skips non-multipart bodies) — but use FormData in production.
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Hospital",
  "lastName": "Staff",
  "email": "requester2@test.com",
  "password": "223456",
  "phoneNumber": "9000000002",
  "bloodGroup": "O+",
  "state": "Telangana",
  "role": "REQUESTER"
}

### Register Donor
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Donor",
  "lastName": "Four",
  "email": "donor13@test.com",
  "password": "1323456",
  "phoneNumber": "9001300002",
  "bloodGroup": "O-",
  "state": "Telangana",
  "role": "DONOR"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email":"admin@test.com",
  "password":"123456"
}

### Check Auth
GET http://localhost:5000/auth/check-auth
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Logout
GET http://localhost:5000/auth/logout
